snippet.textDisplay:
Lalon kobi oshadharon. Ami bhabte pari na jini oshikhito hoe o emni kobita likhte parten uni bhogoban er roop ki bhabe noi. Lalon fokir shomoy er aage eshe din duniya ke shekhate proyash kore chilen. Shei jinish aaj o aamra shikte na pari. 
Lalon Fakir is unmatched. I can come to terms with the fact that an illiterate man made so much sense through eternity, he was the lord dressed as a mere mortal. He was much ahead of his time, but he taught generations the meaning of the word humanity as he despised any form of discrimination and religious grouping. However his lessons are still ignored. Jai guru!!
